Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Perfect access to Wayville Train Station

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The property is still one of the best fringe office buildings with an impressive foyer and internal atrium and fully refurbished amenities.  The available areas are stunning tenancies that have near new fitouts with a mix of workstations, meeting areas and fixed offices.
Located in the heart of the Fringe office market with easy access to the CBD.

Features: 

- On-site parks available. 
- High quality, corporate, modern office space.
- Parkland outlooks.
- Valuable access to the new Wayville train station.

Available Areas:

Ground - 181 sqm (approx)

First - 260.8 sqm (approx)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The recently refurbished 45 Greenhill Road Wayville provides a high level of office accommodation that is part owner occupied. 

Comprising 160 square metres on the ground floor, the space provides a terrific working environment with the bonus of an on-site Funk Cafe. The Cafe includes outdoor seats that along with the pleasant indoor surrounds make for a terrific amenity to tenants.

The fitout is practical and well presented, with a mix of open-plan space, 2 offices, storage and meeting rooms plus a well appointed breakout space

Located in the heart of the fringe market is this well appointed Greenhill Road office space ideal for groups seeking a top quality office space. Maintained to a high standard and afforded with a modern, functional fitout, this space provides excellent natural light, gorgeous leafy surrounds, and overall a fantastic office environment to work in. Level 1, 83 Greenhill Road also boasts a great location, being only 500 metres from the corner of King William & Greenhill Roads, giving easy access to the CBD via trams and public transport.
